data.description: Welcome to this charming two-bedroom, one-bathroom home in the heart of Park Forest, IL.  This beautifully maintained property features a spacious living room with great natural lighting and a recently updated kitchen with all stainless steel appliances, a large family room to the rear of the home with a wood-burning fireplace, and a vast backyard awaiting your vision.  This is perfect as a starter home, a cozy retirement ranch, or anyone looking to downsize.  Easy to show, see today.
